		"    By the Builder this place is going to be the end of me. Do they not know I am a man of thought and introspection who requires peace and quiet if I am to adequately inscribe my thoughts? No great writer ever had to put up with such endless midnight interruptions as I."
		""
		"    I see no sensibility in having that blasted iron wagon rumbling down the "
	}
	"page1_right_title"	:
