	}
	"page2_left_body"	:
	{
		""
		"    I believe I shall be forced to complain directly to the landlord. I must catch him at a moment when that Hales woman and her two brutes are not about. His Lordship is then certain to defer to my confident manner. Just as soon as mother sends me the money to buy a new coat. One must look the part."
